channel.title: [emulous] adding and deleting global objects?
channel.description: ok ive dled hazies official source but it didnt come with global object files, so i downloaded someone elses edited source of this and added the global and world objects files in both .java and .class too my server, does anyone know how too add global objects in these or delete global objects that are currently on the map.
